"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"**WE are ONE**\\n\\nWe will support the Fantom Ecosystem.\\n\\nWe want to demystify decentralized finance.\\n\\nWe will bring a suite of Defi products to the Opera Network and $GHAST will be our utility token. The products and advancements to the protocol will come in the form of Apparitions.\\n\\nThe first of many **Apparitions** will be revealed soon.\\n\\n**Welcome to Spectre**.\\n\\nThis protocol is designed to bring new and innovative features to the Fantom community. Some of these products may exist on other networks, others may not. Some of the products are simple and intuitive while others are more ambitious. These features, upgrades, and innovations will be revealed in due time, in the form of **Apparitions**.\\n\\nA few of our main goals is is to demystify decentralized finance, support financial inclusion, and support [cryptocurrency adoption](https://www.zhihu.com/search?q=cryptocurrency+adoption&search_source=Entity&hybrid_search_source=Entity&hybrid_search_extra=%7B%22sourceType%22%3A%22article%22%2C%22sourceId%22%3A437560363%7D)\\n\\n. Through a combination of education and intuitive-to-use products, we plan to bring low-cost, high-speed defi options to the Fantom community. With our low friction and easy to use dashboard, we anticipate a significant amount of support from newer defi users and hopefully non-crypto natives.\\n\\n## First things first.\\n\\n$GHAST will begin as a fork of $OHM. We will not be “just” another low effort $OHM clone. We also have no intention of being a reserve currency. Information on our tokenomics, initial circulating supply, and distribution model will be released soon. We would love to reveal our first Apparition in full detail, however today we will only announce the following alpha in support of the Fantom Network:\\n\\n**$FTM** will be our primary reserve currency and our pre-sale denomination.\\n\\n**$FTM/$GHAST** will be our first liquidity pair.\\n\\nThe Reserve Stablecoin is still to be determined. In addition to holding stablecoins in our treasury, we will hedge against $FTM market volatility by growing the treasury through \\\\[To be REDACTED\\\\].\\n\\nFuture Apparitions to reveal themselves in due time.\\n\\nMore documents to follow soon\",\"timestamp\":1638792660,\"title\":\"WE are SPECTRE\"},\"digest\":\"sM_gpY0_gI0Dxedd2FXM75030Bvc2ws2qrwsqVv6dRY\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x174459460A65Dac1242793534dAf9502B0168ab0\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"umy3W-gpFNczWpygvYmsmemik2w_OEqLlMJ1e-y6-Zk\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"mJs_eKztyxGUDLFQf8aY5_4Re-Z0TJpqk_1Ht_5T4fs\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"A2KhJqCyOncpXMmUQywzzd81W1X8hORxrIydxEukmc6RgBIQNRBEJO3HuRxlPBIBmQ1hZG1aUkXhwOkqTujLow\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x6ae800a6ebbe71395ac9e48cab517a8bfd793c908728398c842d64f3583a4a727227e9b7396e5b3408db0f4bc0839e423792a06837a37779e4adaeb95ec689851b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"umy3W-gpFNczWpygvYmsmemik2w_OEqLlMJ1e-y6-Zk\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"mJs_eKztyxGUDLFQf8aY5_4Re-Z0TJpqk_1Ht_5T4fs\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"sM_gpY0_gI0Dxedd2FXM75030Bvc2ws2qrwsqVv6dRY\"}"